{"tid":1646062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵又一核彈 ： 搵前線食死貓","createTime":"2019-10-11T06:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T13:42:16.000Z","uid":97448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5249df74ba5ffde9422e1415afcae035304dfa","tid":1646062,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"關於早前有列車喺茘景站炒車，內部嘅調查結果竟然係賴車長無睇燈無睇波口，仲話睇唔清嘅應該叫 控制中心(OCC) 開隧路燈 😕<br />\n<br />\n但早前唔係有消息指出，係 OCC 叫車長衝燈(Pass Signal At Danger)嫁咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果屬實嘅話，究竟而家成個 MTR 車務部係咪為咗保住個車長，就由得件事繼續錯落去？<br />\n<br />\n圖：MTR Secrets<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXFYvJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXFYvJA.jpg&h=9debe7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黨鐵風氣：有鑊就搵前線揹，有功就老屎忽拎<br />\n<br />\n為左唔做臭自己黨鐵同高層個名，有事就搵最底層食<br />\n<br />\n人工又閪<br />\n<br />\n前線同事唔好再沈默啦！</span>"},{"pid":"7f47351d7fd21e4751fe165a2e0ce5bc5f9ed205","tid":1646062,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acc34505d5f30a53db5fc2f59d587f6669707f3","tid":1646062,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c362d3c954a6b6fc593bfa2e958632a30d54c747","tid":1646062,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f632f8cc4c03cad8680ce77ca95fc23aa5544c54","tid":1646062,"uid":97448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"